[en_US]
Massive Mod/Remix Ultra v1.2

Hacker: Jason[FGCH] (thanks for Kim[FGCH]'s technical support)

Reencryption: oak2003(programming) & siromezm(conversion)

Description: 
1. unlocked all characters
2. EXCEED background changed to Street Fighter style
3. select any opponent in console Practise Mode
4. many special move changes (see Chinese description)

[zh_CN]
整体修改/Remix Ultra v1.2

修改者: Jason[FGCH] ( 感谢 Kim[FGCH] 技术支援 )

